<item>
            <title>[LOG4J2-1818] Fix rollover to work when filePattern contains no directory components</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-1818</link>
                <project id="12310790" key="LOG4J2">Log4j 2</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;See &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/logging-log4j2/pull/59&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/logging-log4j2/pull/59&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Prior to this patch, the following config threw NPE at parent.mkdirs() because parent was null when using e.g.:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-xml&quot;&gt;        &amp;lt;RollingRandomAccessFile name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;FILE&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
                                 fileName=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;foo.log&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
                                 filePattern=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;foo-%d{yyyy-MM-dd}-%i.log.gz&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
                                 immediateFlush=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;false&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;while this config did not:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-xml&quot;&gt;        &amp;lt;RollingRandomAccessFile name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;FILE&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
                                 fileName=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;foo.log&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
                                 filePattern=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;./foo-%d{yyyy-MM-dd}-%i.log.gz&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
                                 immediateFlush=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;false&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;e.g. by adding ./ in front of the filePattern value.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
